# SupeRISE CLI Environment Variables
#
# IMPORTANT: All environment variables are OPTIONAL.
# The system has smart defaults and works out of the box.
#
# For persistent configuration, use CLI commands instead:
#   rise sustain config show                    # View current config
#   rise sustain config set <key> <value>       # Set config value
#   rise sustain config edit                    # Interactive editor
#
# See: docs/sustain/CONFIGURATION.md
#
# NOTE: Mock vs Production is determined at BUILD TIME, not runtime.
#   - Production build: bun run build
#   - Test build: bun run build:test

# ===== Optional Environment Variables =====
# These can temporarily override config file values
# All are optional - system works without any of these set

# Cron Mode (optional)
# Values: "dev" or "production"
# Default: "production"
# SUSTAIN_CRON_MODE=dev

# Mock Platform Address (optional, only used in test builds)
# Default: ckt1qrfrwcdnvssswdwpn3s9v8fp87emat306ctjwsm3nmlkjg8qyza2cqgqq8ngrhm6tfxx8qfpjjma3lzasdl47hpz8sfn65a7
# SUPERISE_CLI_MOCK_PLATFORM_ADDRESS=ckt1qzda0cr08m85hc8jlnfp3zzd9me3ls5ne4ejxw

# Mock Balance Settings (optional, only used in test builds)
# Default: initialBalance=10000, decayRate=50
# SUPERISE_CLI_MOCK_INITIAL_BALANCE=10000
# SUPERISE_CLI_MOCK_BALANCE_DECAY_RATE=50

# Platform URLs (optional)
# Defaults: api.superise-openrouter.com, localhost:11434
# SUPERISE_OPENROUTER_BASE_URL=https://api.superise-openrouter.com
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434

# Models Cache TTL (optional, milliseconds)
# Default: 1800000 (30 minutes)
# SUSTAIN_MODELS_CACHE_TTL_MS=1800000
